name: Amazoness Call
desc: Take 1 "Amazoness" card from your Deck, except "Amazoness Call", and either add it to your hand or send it to the GY. You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 "Amazoness" monster you control; this turn, other monsters you control cannot attack, also that monster can attack all monsters your opponent controls, once each. You can only activate 1 "Amazoness Call" per turn.
